metadata.name: Rubik's Retribution
metadata.description:
A sequence of colourful, generative movements, following complicated formulative principles the master Ern≈ë Rubik laid out in his paradoxical cubic creation, widely-known as the Rubik's Cube.

JIT-Formulated

0.1x Raystep Multiplier

4x calculated threadcounts

8x Smoothed-Normals (map-diffused)

SSA024 Ambient Shadowing (Z/R Threshold: 2)

Ama/Bul Box - 2pt AB Scale, 2.48pt BB Scale / 0.03% fold (60 iterations)

Post-processed Hard Shadowing (4pt calc'd length, 1e0 radius, lightfunc cosined)
